posting_body: ['The Retreat is situated in lush natural surroundings, including towering trees and a rippling creek.', 'This beautifully landscaped community is nestled within a cozy neighborhood just moments from bustling downtown Walnut Creek, Broadway Plaza, Iron Horse Trail, Interstate I-680, Highway 24, and the BART station.', 'Our community is within the prestigious Walnut Creek school district.', 'Beautiful views and large apartment spaces at The Retreat!', 'The large refreshing swimming pool and spas are surrounded by lush landscaping and fountains.', 'The Retreat is a pet friendly and smoke free community.', 'Community Amenities', 'Available 24/7 to Assist You • BBQ/Picnic Area • Courtesy Patrol • Package Receiving • Heated Swimming Pool •', 'Spa •', 'Poolside Fire Pit • Tranquil Landscaping with Water Features • Near Public Transportation', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Granite Counter-tops • Stainless Steel Efficient Appliances •', 'Patio/Balcony • Air Conditioner •', 'Dual Pane Windows • Hardwood Inspired Floors', 'Your 4 legged friends are welcome at The Retreat!', 'Pets - Max 2 allowed', 'Comments:', 'Breed restrictions apply.', '\xa0 A deposit and rent charge is required for each pet.', 'Cats -  allowed, Rent $35.00, Deposit $500.00 Dogs -  allowed, Rent $50.00, Deposit $500.00', 'We are located near downtown Walnut Creek!', 'The Retreat at Walnut Creek', '1459 Creekside Dr', 'Walnut Creek, CA 94596', 'Federal law prohibits housing discrimination on the basis of race, color, national origin, religion, sex, familial status, or disability.', '* Prices and availability are subject to change without notice.', 'Open 7 days a week', 'Mon-Fri:', '9AM-6PM', 'Sat - Sun:', '10AM-4PM', 'Call us to schedule a property tour today!', 'Phone:', 'show contact info']
